    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE], the manager, manager of a paper in the town on the-- on the [INAUDIBLE] Drive, and I went there and Egri came to the house.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That close.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I-- we wanted, we arranged through, to the lawyer, he tells us personally, because the lawyer, lawyer arranged it, it has to be done personally, face to face.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "All right, Egri come to the house, come to the-- come to the [INAUDIBLE], and so on.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And what you want to retract and so on?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That's what he told to retract, that my accusation was not true And so on.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was a half-baked nothing.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And sitting face to face with the men, had the same table on one end, me, and the other end, Mrs.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE], Mr.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] sitting the same kitchen, kitchen table.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I couldn't do nothing, because I already know, already knew, that this kind of thing so hot to stuff that I can't point a finger, finger at the-- but when I came to my, came to my book, I went to, went to a lawyer, who was a lawyer about your age, a Jewish lady, for advice.",
      "word_count": 58
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And she told me, look, you can't-- you can't name me.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Said, it might be, and you might be lucky, and I'm almost sure it might be, even could be arranged to have a Jewish judge.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And you might be able what you are saying, that without lawyer, you are ready to stand up relying on your own prestige, that you were an officer in such and such a service, and without lawyer, I make a statement and-- and charge him.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Said, the judge might even accept, but we'll tell the court, you-- we believe you.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But prove it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Because this is the law.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
